Brittany Alexandra Tiplady  is a Canadian actress best known for her role as Jordan Black in the television series Millennium . She won a 1998 Young Artist Award for "Best Performance in a TV Drama Series - Supporting Actress". She also played the role of Maggie in the 2007 film Hot Rod.
Her brother Avery is also a child performer.
title: Brittany Tiplady
